    "IntroductionIn the speculative novel named Snow Crash, the virtual parallel world in which users interact with characters is called the metaverse [1], which has also become the literary Origin of the metaverse mentioned by most scholars.",
    "In the virtual reality field, the initial version of the Metaverse was conceptualised as a network of virtual worlds where avatars could travel between them effortlessly.",
    "This idea was brought to life with Opensim's Hypergrid [2].",
    "The second iteration of the Metaverse in mixed reality is presently being developed to establish a social and immersive VR platform that can function smoothly with massively multiplayer online games, open game worlds, and AR collaboration spaces.",
    "Users will be able to socialize and interact with one another as 3D holograms or avatars in physical or virtual spaces without any limitations, according to this vision [3]."
